{"tid":602512,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"曾是女偶像41歲母激似長澤雅美 21歲法學院大學生打包私奔","createTime":"2018-03-23T05:10:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-23T08:06:46.000Z","uid":9573,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"17ed59cb0bfd3172def87935f0d585636f8d1280","tid":602512,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T05:10:00.000Z","msg":"日本東京一名網友11日發文表示，42歲母親拿走家中200萬元（日幣，約台幣54萬9300元），且和一名21歲法學院男大生私奔，當地綜藝節目《ビビット》22日挖出女生身分，原來她名叫美穗，曾是企劃女團「電波子2〜28号」的成員之一，與老公德永數馬結婚後生下4名孩子。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3180/d3180627.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3180%2Fd3180627.jpg&h=b98c32f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲德永美穗年輕時和長澤雅美有幾分神似。<br />\n<br />\n美穗和21歲男大生鈴木涉大透過網路認識，她曾帶對方到家裡吃飯，讓老公德永數馬見過本人，但席間男大生絲毫不隱藏對她的愛慕，丈夫相當不安、要她和對方斷開聯繫，她還是偷偷地和男大生私下傳訊周日短暫時間有陽光，稍後有一兩陣驟雨，氣溫19至23度。德永數馬得知後火大地說：「我知道你們在幹什麼！」沒想到她一氣之下離家，還一把帶走好幾本存摺。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3162/d3162735.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3162%2Fd3162735.jpg&h=7f5ca263&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲美穗家人懷疑她就是和這名男大生私奔了。<br />\n<br />\n德永數馬和美穗結婚後，共生下3個兒子、1個女兒，10年前因罹患糖尿病失明，生活起居都需要有人24小時照顧，家中經濟並不算寬裕，3個兒子都得靠獎學金負擔大學學費。美穗離家後曾把存摺寄回，但已領走獎學金200萬元（日幣，約台幣54萬9300元），雖然她沒有透露人在哪裡，但從手機簡訊和家裡發現的一封男大生的情書，德永家人相信美穗是和男大生私奔了。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3162/3162736.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3162%2F3162736.jpg&h=0923d4e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼德永美穗兒子透過網路尋母。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3162/d3162734.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3162%2Fd3162734.jpg&h=b3f6a2fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美穗身高約153公分，體重介於約58公斤左右，今年41歲的她出身女團「電波子2〜28号」，年輕時的照片被說激似演員長澤雅美，男大生鈴木涉大年僅21歲，和她的大兒子同齡，目前就讀大二，在學校加入過「捉迷藏社」。"},{"pid":"7f51e19458825fb44e35fa24a116ca817fc98a4e","tid":602512,"uid":80176,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T05:13:38.000Z","msg":"她還是偷偷地和男大生私下傳訊周日短暫時間有陽光，稍後有一兩陣驟雨，氣溫19至23度。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5813f1c5e4adb139ace1402cecc47c3bda8587f","tid":602512,"uid":91982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T05:19:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c0cde6b3467634cc5a8a91f6191ccecc21bae6f5","tid":602512,"uid":46587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f51e19458825fb44e35fa24a116ca817fc98a4e","tid":602512,"uid":80176,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T05:13:38.000Z","msg":"她還是偷偷地和男大生私下傳訊周日短暫時間有陽光，稍後有一兩陣驟雨，氣溫19至23度。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T05:20:29.000Z","msg":"樓豬個名"},{"pid":"941867f98c2754af77125713483cbe2f10112e59","tid":602512,"uid":18568,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T05:23:47.000Z","msg":"在學校加入過「捉迷藏社」。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幾得意"},{"pid":"260484df47b3e55251ef38eeaeb711359d6a21d9","tid":602512,"uid":42487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T05:25:19.000Z","msg":"個細路識食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f3d01fc3359dda0f3bbc53b5994c7c94930bb8b","tid":602512,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T05:35:15.000Z","msg":"hallelujah chance<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"450efee93a31fe1055c811a779d1c0ccca40ac95","tid":602512,"uid":27064,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"941867f98c2754af77125713483cbe2